# Vedisha Marketing Project Rules

## Tech Stack
- Static HTML/CSS/JS
- Minified assets for production (.min.css, .min.js)
- Images in WebP format
- Shared Header/Footer injected via js/header.js and js/footer.js

## SEO Standards
- All pages must have unique <title> and <meta name="description">.
- Keywords should focus on "Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar", "Aurangabad", and "Maharashtra".
- Maintain JSON-LD schema on key pages.

## Performance
- Always use loading="lazy" for images.
- Keep Interaction Latency low by minimizing heavy JS.
- Convert all new images to WebP.

## Branding
- Primary Color Theme: Sky Blue (#0ea5e9) and Ocean Blue (#3b82f6).
- Secondary: Light Sky Blue (#7dd3fc).
- Font: Outfit (Display), Plus Jakarta Sans (Body).
